    <item>
      <title>随着关系改善，中国取消对澳大利亚葡萄酒的关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/china-scraps-tariffs-on-australian-wine-as-relations-improve</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国取消了对澳大利亚葡萄酒出口的惩罚性关税，标志着对堪培拉长达三年的贸易压力运动的结束，并为这个价值数十亿美元的行业复兴带来了希望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/china-scraps-tariffs-on-australian-wine-as-relations-improve</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 07:02:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
